Texts.Chs:
纤维、维生素和矿物质的良好来源。在当地由进口原料制成。非常适合消化红肉和其他肉类。否则，它反而会消化你，尽管很缓慢。
^green;类型：素食^reset;
Texts.Eng:
A great source of Fiber, Vitamins, and Minerals. Made from local and imported ingredients. Excellent for digesting red and other meats. Otherwise, it digests you instead, ever so slightly.
^green;Type: Herbivore^reset;
